channel.title: Need help with VPS
channel.description:
Need help urgently please.
I bought a vps lately and im trying to run my rsps on it.. I have downloaded no ip and opened a TCP and UDP on 43594. Then went on to Runelocus and checked if server was online when my no ip account was running too. What else did i miss or did i not do so it says `Online` as the server ip.
Skype: RspsSupport
